data.description: Come see this great home in Culpepper Landing featuring an open layout, massive two-car garage, gas oven, downstairs office with custom built in cabinets, & tall ceilings throughout. The home has a wonderful kitchen including a large island with quartz countertops, recessed lights, plenty of cabinet space with a separate pantry, & stainless steel appliances including a gas oven. Kitchen overlooks the dining room & living room area with fireplace. The laundry is located on the first floor near the half bathroom. Second floor has 3 bedrooms including primary bedroom with massive walk-in closet & en suite bathroom with dual vanity, linen closet, & walk-in shower. Hallway bath & attic access complete the second floor. The driveway is located in the back of the home, along with an attached garage with ample storage built in. Fully fenced yard with white picket fencing. Culpepper Landing community boasts multiple parks, dog parks, fitness center, clubhouse, pool, walking trails, & ponds.
